messages: a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:32): hello
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:32): Tell me a dream you have had please?
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:33): a dream? a good one or a bad one
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:33): Either one is fine :)
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:34): i have had a dream where i was naked and flying above the city where i live
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:34): what about you?
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:34): I had one where I was fighting.
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:34): could you land that solid punch?
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:35): Heh, I ended by smashing the guys who were attacking me in the face with my keys.
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:35): Then their sister, who's been trying to intervene the whole fight, pulls me off.
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:36): And I wake up with my fly undone.
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:36): hahahahah
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:36): thats pretty crazy
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:36): did you know the guys you were fighting?
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:37): I was watching the one guy do parkour, and said I wished I could do it, and he attacked me, then his friend hit me as well.
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:37): I ran away, they grabbed my keys,we played tug of war, and I smashed them with my keys till they fell down.
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:38): What do you think it means?
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:38): hmmmm, it could mean a lot of things i guess...
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:38): do you like parkour? want to learn?
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:38): I do want to learn.
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:39): hmmmm maybe that had something to do with it
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:39): most of my dreams are kind of weird
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:39): Yeah
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:40): What's another of yours?
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:40): i was being held down,
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:40): by two of my ex girlfriends
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:40): and they were cutting me
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:40): i couldnt get away
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:41): reminds me of a bizarre one I had as a kid
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:41): There were these people, and they stepped on a trap.
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:42): They were put into a hole, and couldn't get out.
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:42): All they had to eat was burger king, but for some reason they couldn't crawl out of the drive through door.
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:42): WHAAAT
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:42): hahahah
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:43): thats crazy
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:43): They were all fine, but they would never leave, and the situation would never change
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:43): Yeah
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:44): tell me another one
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:44): Let's see
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:44): My hair was long and white, and I was flying.
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:44): I was in a sphere, and flying within the sphere.
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:45): And somehow the sphere was a dragon.
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:45): And I pushed it forward a little bit, and woke up.
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:45): did you feel the push?
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:45): I was the push
a3b27b6f8c21f4f20f430bea52e2b584 (18:47): i bet that was intense
10d565a34118f6cdbc16e6ecfc188b9d (18:47): Yeah
